#### Summary

I am not sure this is a bug, but I wanted to report it nonetheless.

It took me some time to understand the logic of reporting the retried test only once in #6742.

Only the last attempt gets reported (I've been looking at JUnit and OTR logs); this way, however, we lose information about the reasons earlier attempts failed, which may be relevant to investigate. Example: the last failure may be a normal assertion failure, hence I'd be looking into fixing my code, but the previous ones may be infra related and I will not know I have infra problems.

Apart from the above, the reported duration of the test IMHO should be the sum of all attempts, not just the duration of the last one. The runner total execution time does not match the sum of all the tests.

Example:

with a test like
```
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace Drupal\Tests\Core\Layout;

use Drupal\Tests\UnitTestCase;
use PHPUnit\Framework\Attributes\DataProvider;
use PHPUnit\Framework\Attributes\Retry;
use PHPUnit\Framework\TestCase;

class LayoutDefaultTest extends TestCase {

  #[DataProvider('providerTestBuild')]
  #[Retry(5)]
  public function testBuild(int $wait): void {
    sleep($wait);
    $this->assertFalse(TRUE);
  }

  public static function providerTestBuild(): array {
    $data = [];
    $data['foo'] = [1];
    $data['bar'] = [2];
    return $data;
  }

}

```

running `phpunit --log-junit junit.log --log-otr otr.log LayoutDefaultTest.php `

we get 
```
PHPUnit 13.3-dev by Sebastian Bergmann and contributors.

Runtime:       PHP 8.5.6
Configuration: /Users/xxxx/Dev/drupal/core/phpunit.xml.dist

FF                                                                  2 / 2 (100%)

Time: 00:15.106, Memory: 20.00 MB

There were 2 failures:

1) Drupal\Tests\Core\Layout\LayoutDefaultTest::testBuild@foo with data (1)
Failed asserting that true is false.

/Users/xxxx/Dev/drupal/core/tests/Drupal/Tests/Core/Layout/LayoutDefaultTest.php:18

2) Drupal\Tests\Core\Layout\LayoutDefaultTest::testBuild@bar with data (2)
Failed asserting that true is false.

/Users/xxxx/Dev/drupal/core/tests/Drupal/Tests/Core/Layout/LayoutDefaultTest.php:18

FAILURES!
Tests: 2, Assertions: 2, Failures: 2.

```

the runner reports 15 seconds elapsed (which is correct). Junit reports a total elapsed of 3 seconds (ie. the sum of the two last attempts of each test case). OTR reports a total of 15 seconds and the suites time are correct too, but the individual test cases do not match the suite time.

